    "en": "Developed in the Vendée region of France before World War I from the larger Grand Griffon Vendéen. Selectively bred down in size by the Comte d'Elva to create a smaller faster hound for hunting medium game like hare and fox. Nearly decimated by World Wars but carefully restored",
    "zh": "一战前在法国旺代地区由大型旺代格里芬犬培育而成。经埃尔瓦伯爵选择性小型化选育，创造更小更快的猎犬用于猎兔狐等中型猎物。两次世界大战中几乎灭绝但经精心恢复。"
  },
